data.text:
⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

Cristi has been a godsend for my business. Along with her sister, she has created and administrated my company web site which serves hundreds of student tenants and their families. The web design is epic, and even my competitors have begrudgingly told me they envy the design and creativity that Cristi and he sister harnessed. Because of this work, my web traffic is higher, and my tenants have a user friendly place to gather information or communicate directly with me.
